Haaay i miss you so much bby huhuhu. After more than a week together, these past three days have been filled with loneliness and missing you all the time. Just thinking about how much your presence will help me makes me miss you all the more.

Tas isama mo pa yung kay mama huhuhu, i need your cuddles bby huhuhu. Nakakastress kase and nakaka anxiety talaga huhuhu. I need my comfort person mwaaaa. I love you so much bby!! I can't wait to see you tomorrow!

Thank you too for trying your best to always support me, and validate my feelings, and help me feel less anxious. I'm really lucky to have someone like you by my side!
